Package: revtools
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2018-01-31
Title: Tools to Support Evidence Synthesis in R
Author: Martin J. Westgate <martinjwestgate@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Martin J. Westgate <martinjwestgate@gmail.com>
Description: Tools to support literature review and evidence synthesis in R. Includes functions to import references, remove duplicates, and interactively select or exclude individual articles.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports: ade4, plotly, shiny, shinycssloaders, shinydashboard, SnowballC, stringdist, tm, topicmodels, viridisLite, methods, modeltools
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
